Package: debocker
Architecture: all
Depends: docker.io,
         python3 (>= 3.3),
         python3-click,
         ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${python3:Depends}
Description: docker-powered package builder for Debian
 debocker builds Debian packages using docker. It is also capable to
 create bundles that can be shared to build the same package on
 different nodes.
